snippet: Jimmy Walker pulled away from the pack with three straight birdies on the back nine and closed with a seven-under-par 63 to win the Sony Open in Honolulu.
abstract: Jimmy Walker wins Sony Open in Honolulu for his second PGA Tour victory in his last six starts; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Jimmy Walker pulled away from the pack with three straight birdies on the back nine and closed with a seven-under-par 63 to win the Sony Open in Honolulu.
